<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 mǎ qí dùn de hū shēng, yuè lái yuè qīng xī. qiáng yuán tān tā xiǎo yáng shī mí.
 shén de pū rén nǎ, nǐ xīn kě céng zhe jí? fù qīn de yǎn jīng zhèng zài wàng zhe nǐ.
 yáng wú mù rén jiù chéng wèi lǔ wù, mù rén ruǎn ruò yì duān jiù xí jī.
 shén de pū rén nǎ, zhǔ yǐ tuō fù gěi nǐ. dào lù qí qū, zhǔ bì bāng zhù nǐ.</lyrics>
<title>mǎ qí dùn de hū shēng 迦南750</title>
<hymn_number>750</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>